# Cautious Resq Ready Now

This repository stores the blueprints and prompts for the **Cautious Resq Ready Now** application built on Base44.

**App URL:** [https://cautious-resq-ready-now.base44.app](https://cautious-resq-ready-now.base44.app)

## 📋 App Blueprint & Core Prompts

### Master Generation Prompt
> Paste the exact primary text/prompt you used in Base44 to generate this app here. E.g., "Build a search and rescue coordination application with real-time status updates..."

### Pages & Structure
* **Dashboard:** Home screen displaying recent requests and active rescues.
* **Request Form:** Allows users to log incident locations and urgency levels.
* **Admin panel:** For dispatching teams and updating ticket status.

## 🛠️ Data Model / Schema
* **Incidents Table:** `id`, `location`, `status` (Pending, Active, Resolved), `reported_by`, `timestamp`.
* **Rescuers Table:** `id`, `name`, `availability`, `assigned_incident_id`.
